<item>
            <title>[HBASE-34] Set memcache flush size per column</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-34</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The amount of memory taken by the memcache before a flush is currently a global parameter.  It should be configurable per-table.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12383959">HBASE-34</key>
